			<attribute id="HowToTrigger" type="LSString" value="- Load up GustavDev/CTY_Main_A&#xD;&#xA;- Use ReCon command &quot;oe MT_Baptism&quot; and then &quot;goto -1259 2 466&quot;. The cultists will appear and start their chant." />
